data.description: Beachside, 2-story townhome, south of 5th Avenue. Steps away from the beach via pedestrian crosswalk, this gem host high ceilings with skylights providing tons of natural light. Kitchen, dining room, living room, spare bedroom and screened-in porch all overlook the beautiful backyard that includes community pool. Downstairs includes full bath between two bedrooms, plenty of closet space, and laundry off kitchen. Owner suite encompasses entire upstairs and includes spacious open area perfect for an office. Bath offers large tub, separate shower and two sizable walk-in closets. Additional amenities include garage with workspace, peaks of the ocean from private balcony upstairs and just a short drive to 5th Ave dining and shopping.
